john l thornton  wikipedia john l thornton from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search john lawson thornton born  january   age  nationality american alma mater harvard college ba oxford university bj mj yale university ma john lawson thornton born january   is a professor and director of the global leadership program at tsinghua university in beijing he is also executive chairman of barrick gold corporation and nonexecutive chairman of pinebridge investments thornton retired as president of goldman sachs in  contents  early life and education  career  interest in china  personal life  references  external links early life and educationedit thornton is the son of john v thornton a former vice chairman of the consolidated edison company and edna lawson thornton a lawyer he attended the hotchkiss school and would later serve as president of the school’s board of trustees thornton received a bachelors degree in history from harvard college in  a bama in jurisprudence from oxford university in  and an ma in public and private management from the yale school of management in  he was awarded an honorary doctorate from the bank street college of education in  thornton was elected a fellow of the american academy of arts and sciences in  and an honorary fellow of st john’s college oxford university in  careeredit thornton joined goldman sachs in  and became a partner at age  in  he founded and developed goldman sachs european mergers and acquisitions business he first began work in london in  and served as coceo of goldman sachs international in london from  to  thornton was chairman of goldman sachs asia from  to  where he expanded the firms regional franchise during the asian financial crisis he announced his retirement from goldman sachs in  to take up an academic position in china although he would remain an adviser on issues related to china according to the new york times thorntons decision to retire was prompted by a recognition that mr paulson who is  plans to remain goldmans leader for at least three to five more years delaying mr thorntons expected promotion in  barrick gold faced criticism over thorntons compensation following the company’s decision to award him an  million signon bonus according to the globe and mail the company later acknowledged shareholder concerns and vowed to make changes to its compensation practices at the company’s  annual general meeting more than  of barrick’s shareholders approved the company’s compensation practices thornton has served on the boards of many large public companies including china unicom hsbc industrial and commercial bank of china intel and news corporation he is currently executive chairman of barrick gold corporation a member of the board of ford motor company and also serves as nonexecutive chairman of pinebridge investments he is also chairman of the board of trustees of the brookings institution in  institutional investor magazine named john thornton one of forty individuals who have had the greatest influence in shaping global financial markets over the past forty years he received the  intercollegiate tennis association ita achievement award which every year honors one past participant in collegiate tennis who has made unique contributions to society as well as achieving excellence in their careers thornton appeared on the national post’s  power list of the most influential people shaping canadian business the newspaper noted thornton has “overseen a massive overhaul at torontobased barrick” following which the company “has shed billions of dollars of debt and generated excellent financial results interest in chinaedit thorntons interest in china stretches to the s where he helped build goldmans presence in asia at the time of his retirement goldman had become the lead underwriter for major chinese stateowned companies in  thornton funded the establishment of the john l thornton china center at the brookings institution in  he also became a member of the international advisory council of the chinese sovereign wealth fund china investment corporation he supported the launch of the schwarzman scholarship in  attending its launch at tsinghua university and serving as an honorary board member in  he was awarded the friendship award of the people’s republic of china the highest honor accorded to a nonchinese citizen the chinese government also named him as one of fifteen ‘foreign experts’ who have made the most significant contribution to china’s development over the past three decades personal lifeedit thornton is married to margaret bradham thornton they have four children referencesedit  nndb executive profile  john l thornton   school of public policy and managementtsinghua university wwwtsinghuaeducn retrieved    barrick gold corporation  company  management wwwbarrickcom retrieved    john l thornton  pinebridge investments wwwpinebridgecom retrieved    httpswwwwsjcomarticlessb  httpswwwnytimescombusinessjohnvthorntonconedexecutiveisdeadhtmlr  httpswwwnytimescomstylemissthorntontowedjosephdowninghtml  httpwwwhotchkissorgabouthotchkissabouthotchkisshotchkisstrusteesindexaspx  httpwwwbrookingseduaboutmediarelationsnewsreleasesthornton  httpsmcomwpcontentuploadsmaaasannouncesclassoffellowspdf  httpswwwsjcoxacukhonoraryandemeritusfellowshtml  a b c httpswwwnytimescombusinesscopresidentatgoldmanannounceshisretirementhtmlpagewantedall  httpwwwtheglobeandmailcomreportonbusinessindustrynewsenergyandresourcesbarricktorevisecompensationplanasshareholdersvotenoarticle  httpswwwreuterscomarticleusbarrickgoldresultsagmiduskcnxnyktypecompanynews  httpwwwbarrickcominvestorsnewsnewsdetailsbarrickannounceselectionofdirectorsdefaultaspx  john l thornton  pinebridge investments wwwpinebridgecom retrieved    ford online annual report   board of directors and executives corporatefordcom retrieved    barrick gold corporation  company  management wwwbarrickcom retrieved    httpwwwuscpforgvthortonbiohtml  httpwwwitatenniscomassetsitaasse