e citizen the chinese government also named him as one of fifteen ‘foreign experts’ who have made the most significant contribution to china’s development over the past three decades personal lifeedit thornton is married to margaret bradham thornton they have four children referencesedit  nndb executive profile  john l thornton   school of public policy and managementtsinghua university wwwtsinghuaeducn retrieved    barrick gold corporation  company  management wwwbarrickcom retrieved    john l thornton  pinebridge investments wwwpinebridgecom retrieved    httpswwwwsjcomarticlessb  httpswwwnytimescombusinessjohnvthorntonconedexecutiveisdeadhtmlr  httpswwwnytimescomstylemissthorntontowedjosephdowninghtml  httpwwwhotchkissorgabouthotchkissabouthotchkisshotchkisstrusteesindexaspx  httpwwwbrookingseduaboutmediarelationsnewsreleasesthornton  httpsmcomwpcontentuploadsmaaasannouncesclassoffellowspdf  httpswwwsjcoxacukhonoraryandemeritusfellowshtml  a b c httpswwwnytimescombusinesscopresidentatgoldmanannounceshisretirementhtmlpagewantedall  httpwwwtheglobeandmailcomreportonbusinessindustrynewsenergyandresourcesbarricktorevisecompensationplanasshareholdersvotenoarticle  httpswwwreuterscomarticleusbarrickgoldresultsagmiduskcnxnyktypecompanynews  httpwwwbarrickcominvestorsnewsnewsdetailsbarrickannounceselectionofdirectorsdefaultaspx  john l thornton  pinebridge investments wwwpinebridgecom retrieved    ford online annual report   board of directors and executives corporatefordcom retrieved    barrick gold corporation  company  management wwwbarrickcom retrieved    httpwwwuscpforgvthortonbiohtml  httpwwwitatenniscomassetsitaassetspdftennislifearticlesdecpdf  httpbusinessfinancialpostcomfeaturesthepowerlistmoversandshakerswerebuzzingabout  about  john l thornton china center the brookings institution   archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved    httpwwwtsinghuaeducnpublishjjhenhtml  httpwwwssptsinghuaeducncolumnaboutus  httpcmssemtsinghuaeducnsemcmsnewshtmtempconte